snippet.title: Math Muncher | Gameplay Trailer | Wishlist now on Steam
snippet.description:
Announcing Math Muncher, a relaxing block-pushing puzzle game where you do math and feed the hungry evil that is the Math Muncher.
The game is releasing in February 2025 on PC via Steam, wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3450940/Math_Muncher/
